Class GraphWalk

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.uni_stuttgart.informatik.canu.mobisim.core.ExtensionModule
      • de.uni_stuttgart.informatik.canu.mobisim.mobilitymodels.Movement
        • de.uni_stuttgart.informatik.canu.mobisim.mobilitymodels.RandomWaypointWalk
          • de.uni_stuttgart.informatik.canu.mobisim.mobilitymodels.GraphWalk
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    NotificationListener, XMLStreamable

    public class GraphWalk
extends RandomWaypointWalk
    This class implements the Graph Walk Mobility Model

    Patches:

    Version 1.2 by Jerome Haerri (haerri@ieee.org) on 08/22/2005:
         The Graph Walk Mobility Model is able to load a graph from a SpatialModel extension. By doing so, The Graph Walk Mobility Model may be used with a SpaceGraph extension (a random graph generator).

    Version:
    1.2
    Author:
    1.0-1.1 Illya Stepanov, 1.2 Jerome Haerri
